description: Shannon and her new teeth are back with boof queen AG because, of course, the girls are going to give you a recap on their time at Coachella and the highly anticipated and talked about Revolve Festival. They give you the nitty-gritty about the festival and answer all your burning questions. Which famous influencer blocked Shannon? What happened when they ran into her? How did Shan attempt to apologize? What famous comedian alsooooo has her blocked? Shannon takes a drug then loses AG and the girls give you an update on Funny Guy and his dick skin... or lack thereof? Who knows - not Shannon. This and more in Episode 5 of Probably a Podcast - Blockchella
